        <h3>Cleanser</h3>
        <p>
  If there's one thing that's essential to your skin care routine, it's a cleanser. It should be the first step of your skin care routine every night and every morning.

  But what is a cleanser? Simply put, a cleanser rids your skin of makeup, impurities, dirt, oil, pollution and more. Skin needs to be cleansed regularly day and night, as well as after a rigorous workout. Keeping your pores clear can help you prevent and treat issues like acne, as well as prep your face for other products in your skin care regimen. </p>
